title: What does this thing mean? :O

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: So i was playing a ranked flex match and at the 25min mark i saw this thing? What is it? looks like a blue sword :O

replies.body: lol its a part of the new jg it shows the fall of the old assassins
I might be wrong, but it looks like Shen's spirit sword.

That is more purple I believe...
Could be a teaser for a new champ?
I don't have a clue...I have never noticed it before.
